exaile (0.2.5) dapper; urgency=low
  * many drag and drop tweaks
  * drag and drop now works from the file panel
  * podcasts now have to be downloaded before they can be played
  * added "repeat" and "shuffle" checkboxes above playback controls
  * added rating dropdown for current playing track above playlist
  * added queue count indicator to the right of toggle boxes
  * added locale switcher to preferences

 -- Adam Olsen <arolsen@gmail.com>  Thu, 12 Oct  2006 08:11:00 -7000

exaile (0.2.4) stable; urgency=low
  * use gamin to monitor directories
  * removed automatic reload of collection tree on scan
  * integrate streamripper
  * fixed options, made --help work
  * all open playlists can now be reopened when exaile opens
  * fixed some problems with the OSD preferences
  * renaming of open tabs
  * switched lyrics servers to lyrc.com.ar

